</span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/502eebe5b3cdedf55c4ce7337e0983b2/c2339/sa-yes-community-1.jpg 186w,\n/static/502eebe5b3cdedf55c4ce7337e0983b2/b97a3/sa-yes-community-1.jpg 372w,\n/static/502eebe5b3cdedf55c4ce7337e0983b2/1b3d6/sa-yes-community-1.jpg 743w,\n/static/502eebe5b3cdedf55c4ce7337e0983b2/87945/sa-yes-community-1.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 743px) 100vw, 743px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 743px) 100vw, 743px\" srcSet=\"/static/502eebe5b3cdedf55c4ce7337e0983b2/c2339/sa-yes-community-1.jpg 186w,\n/static/502eebe5b3cdedf55c4ce7337e0983b2/b97a3/sa-yes-community-1.jpg 372w,\n/static/502eebe5b3cdedf55c4ce7337e0983b2/1b3d6/sa-yes-community-1.jpg 743w,\n/static/502eebe5b3cdedf55c4ce7337e0983b2/87945/sa-yes-community-1.jpg 1024w\" src=\"/static/502eebe5b3cdedf55c4ce7337e0983b2/1b3d6/sa-yes-community-1.jpg\" alt=\"SA YES 2017 Taste of Education Dinner\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/502eebe5b3cdedf55c4ce7337e0983b2/c2339/sa-yes-community-1.jpg 186w,\n/static/502eebe5b3cdedf55c4ce7337e0983b2/b97a3/sa-yes-community-1.jpg 372w,\n/static/502eebe5b3cdedf55c4ce7337e0983b2/1b3d6/sa-yes-community-1.jpg 743w,\n/static/502eebe5b3cdedf55c4ce7337e0983b2/87945/sa-yes-community-1.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 743px) 100vw, 743px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 743px) 100vw, 743px\" srcset=\"/static/502eebe5b3cdedf55c4ce7337e0983b2/c2339/sa-yes-community-1.jpg 186w,\n/static/502eebe5b3cdedf55c4ce7337e0983b2/b97a3/sa-yes-community-1.jpg 372w,\n/static/502eebe5b3cdedf55c4ce7337e0983b2/1b3d6/sa-yes-community-1.jpg 743w,\n/static/502eebe5b3cdedf55c4ce7337e0983b2/87945/sa-yes-community-1.jpg 1024w\" src=\"/static/502eebe5b3cdedf55c4ce7337e0983b2/1b3d6/sa-yes-community-1.jpg\" alt=\"SA YES 2017 Taste of Education Dinner\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span><br />\n&nbsp;<br />\nFor 20 years, SA YES has hosted their annual Taste of Education dinner and Golf Classic which raise funds to give students and community groups in San Antonio needed education support with school supplies and grants throughout Bexar County. Each year, SA YES selects numerous elementary schools in San Antonio and supplies every student in those schools with a free packet of school supplies. These school supplies give children in title one elementary schools the basics they need to excel in class. This year, SA YES plans to give out supplies to 26,000 children in San Antonio!<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\nThe PM Group has been the agency of record for SA YES for 20 years.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<span class=\"wp-image-2053 aligncenter inline-gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;max-width:100%;width:750px\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width:100%;padding-bottom:66.48936170212765%\"></span><img aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" alt=\"\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0;transition-delay:500ms\"/><picture><source srcSet=\"/static/0e33569bf8aa805f1039ab992253e67c/20e77/sa-yes-community-2.jpg 188w,\n/static/0e33569bf8aa805f1039ab992253e67c/f21ed/sa-yes-community-2.jpg 375w,\n/static/0e33569bf8aa805f1039ab992253e67c/88df8/sa-yes-community-2.jpg 750w,\n/static/0e33569bf8aa805f1039ab992253e67c/87945/sa-yes-community-2.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\"/><img sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" srcSet=\"/static/0e33569bf8aa805f1039ab992253e67c/20e77/sa-yes-community-2.jpg 188w,\n/static/0e33569bf8aa805f1039ab992253e67c/f21ed/sa-yes-community-2.jpg 375w,\n/static/0e33569bf8aa805f1039ab992253e67c/88df8/sa-yes-community-2.jpg 750w,\n/static/0e33569bf8aa805f1039ab992253e67c/87945/sa-yes-community-2.jpg 1024w\" src=\"/static/0e33569bf8aa805f1039ab992253e67c/88df8/sa-yes-community-2.jpg\" alt=\"SA YES 2017 Golf Classic Event Photo\" loading=\"eager\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transition:opacity 500ms\"/></picture><noscript><picture><source srcset=\"/static/0e33569bf8aa805f1039ab992253e67c/20e77/sa-yes-community-2.jpg 188w,\n/static/0e33569bf8aa805f1039ab992253e67c/f21ed/sa-yes-community-2.jpg 375w,\n/static/0e33569bf8aa805f1039ab992253e67c/88df8/sa-yes-community-2.jpg 750w,\n/static/0e33569bf8aa805f1039ab992253e67c/87945/sa-yes-community-2.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" /><img loading=\"eager\" sizes=\"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px\" srcset=\"/static/0e33569bf8aa805f1039ab992253e67c/20e77/sa-yes-community-2.jpg 188w,\n/static/0e33569bf8aa805f1039ab992253e67c/f21ed/sa-yes-community-2.jpg 375w,\n/static/0e33569bf8aa805f1039ab992253e67c/88df8/sa-yes-community-2.jpg 750w,\n/static/0e33569bf8aa805f1039ab992253e67c/87945/sa-yes-community-2.jpg 1024w\" src=\"/static/0e33569bf8aa805f1039ab992253e67c/88df8/sa-yes-community-2.jpg\" alt=\"SA YES 2017 Golf Classic Event Photo\" style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;opacity:1;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center\"/></picture></noscript></span><br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<strong>About The PM Group:</strong> The PM Group was founded in 1988. Over the past 29 years, the agency has continued to grow and is currently listed as San Antonio’s Largest Advertising Agency by the <em>San Antonio Business Journal</em>. The PM Group’s client roster spans various industries including automotive, CPG, entertainment and sports marketing, legal, business services, non-profit, real estate and fitness. In addition, the agency hosts an annual Charity Gala that to date raised over $1 million for local San Antonio area non-profit organizations.</p>\n","title":"SA YES Celebrates 20th Year of Community Work","seo":{"breadcrumbs":[{"text":"SA YES Celebrates 20th Year of Community Work","url":"/sa-yes-celebrates-20th-year-of-community-work/"}],"title":"SA YES Celebrate 20th Year of Community Work | The PM Group","metaDesc":"The San Antonio Youth Educational Support (SA YES) celebrates their 20th year of community work in Bexar County, providing supplies to elementary schools.","focuskw":"sa yes","metaKeywords":"","metaRobotsNoindex":"index","metaRobotsNofollow":"follow","opengraphTitle":"SA YES Celebrate 20th Year of Community Work | The PM Group","opengraphDescription":"The San Antonio Youth Educational Support (SA YES) celebrates their 20th year of community work in Bexar County, providing supplies to elementary schools.","opengraphImage":{"altText":"SA YES 2017 Golf Classic Event Photo","sourceUrl":"https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/sa-yes-community-2.jpg","srcSet":"https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/sa-yes-community-2-300x200.jpg 300w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/sa-yes-community-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://thepmgroup.flywheelsites.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/sa-yes-community-2.jpg 1024w"},"twitterTitle":"","twitterDescription":"","twitterImage":null,"canonical":"/sa-yes-celebrates-20th-year-of-community-work/","cornerstone":false,"schema":{"raw":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@graph\":[{\"@type\":\"WebSite\",\"@id\":\"/#website\",\"url\":\"/\",\"name\":\"The PM Group\",\"description\":\"San Antonio\\u2019s Largest Advertising and Marketing Agency\",\"potentialAction\":[{\"@type\":\"SearchAction\",\"target\":{\"@type\":\"EntryPoint\",\"urlTemplate\":\"/?s={search_term_string}\"},\"query-input\":\"required name=search_term_string\"}],\"inLanguage\":\"en-US\"},{\"@type\":\